flowchart LR
    A[Pick random\nbrowser UA] --> B[Send request]
    B --> C{Status?}
    C -->|200| D[Process items\nKeep current UA]
    D --> B
    C -->|403| E[Swap to\ndifferent UA]
    E --> F{Retries\nleft?}
    F -->|Yes| B
    F -->|No| G[Report failure]

